room_title: Escape room "Murder 101" by New Smyrna Beach Escape Room in Daytona Beach
room_address: 116 Canal St New Smyrna Beach, FL 32168
room_description:
An exciting two room game that brings you and your CSI team in to help solve a series of grisly murders! Finding evidence and clues in both the detective's office and in the crime scene itself will keep you rushing to beat the clock!
Warning: graphic crime scene and photos.
